we will know whats running inside the container
with the following commands

1.docker container top-------gives all the process running inside the container
2.docker container inspect---gives all data about the container in JSON format
3. docker container stats  --- gives live cpu,memory,disk,network usage

examples of using these commands

docker container container_name/id top

docker container container_name/id stats---live H/W usage

docker container inspect container_name/id   -----all data in JSON format

